title: Ep.29: 1-10 Mock Draft, AFC West Bold Prediction, NBA Play In, Tyreek Hill In Miami, Tua, and Much More!
description: Mock draft #1 is complete! Were releasing our mock draft 10 picks at a time. The AFC west is loaded with talent and the Chiefs trading Tyreek may have lost them some power in that extremely tough division. Will Shaqstrodomis and Griffin be right about the Lakers if they can get into the play in tournament? Tua was throwing to a track team at Alabama and now he is labeled as a guy with no arm. Am I missing something? Tune in to find out!!!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
